Term::CallEditor
==========================

This module calls an external editor with an optional text message and
returns data from the editor as a file handle. For more documentation,
consult the POD in Term/CallEditor.pm.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

File::Temp

